fraud ring or something?

799
00:52:56,818 --> 00:52:58,955
If it wasn't for me,
you would've killed someone.

800
00:52:59,214 --> 00:53:00,811
You're not in your right mind.

801
00:53:01,706 --> 00:53:03,013
You're crazy.

802
00:53:05,861 --> 00:53:08,314
Did you do it because of that
motorcycle accident back then?

803
00:53:11,643 --> 00:53:14,224
What do we do, Yoobum?
I think the police is coming.

804
00:53:17,584 --> 00:53:19,772
-I'm going crazy.
-Gosh!

805
00:53:20,103 --> 00:53:22,088
He'll find out that
I bought that motorcycle.

806
00:53:33,382 --> 00:53:35,245
When the police come, just beg.

807
00:53:35,542 --> 00:53:37,630
Just say that you're sorry and
that you'll pay for the damages.

808
00:53:37,715 --> 00:53:39,216
What are you talking about?

809
00:53:39,584 --> 00:53:41,531
You drove the motorcycle,
so why do I have to pay for the damages?

810
00:53:42,317 --> 00:53:43,341
Tell them that you drove the motorcycle.

811
00:53:43,657 --> 00:53:44,603
That makes more sense.

812
00:53:44,688 --> 00:53:46,089
Are you saying that you're going to lie?

813
00:53:46,851 --> 00:53:48,392
No, Jaechan...

814
00:53:48,761 --> 00:53:50,945
I'm just saying that I'll tell
the story that makes more sense.

815
00:53:51,030 --> 00:53:52,459
To be frank...

816
00:53:55,044 --> 00:53:56,743
...it makes more sense
that you cause this accident than me.

817
00:54:00,045 --> 00:54:01,284
What makes more sense?

818
00:54:01,484 --> 00:54:02,851
You're the one who caused the accident!

819
00:54:02,951 --> 00:54:05,852
I'm going to tell the truth
when the police comes.

820
00:54:07,851 --> 00:54:08,686
Really?

821
00:54:21,851 --> 00:54:23,363
I'm going to say that
you drove the motorcycle.

822
00:54:24,084 --> 00:54:24,818
Yoobum!

823
00:54:24,918 --> 00:54:26,713
There's no witness...

824
00:54:28,473 --> 00:54:30,133
...and you and I are the only ones here.

825
00:54:37,017 --> 00:54:37,934
I'm curious.

826
00:54:39,284 --> 00:54:40,531
Who will...

827
00:54:42,119 --> 00:54:43,343
...the police believe in?

828
00:54:52,450 --> 00:54:54,191
I almost killed someone?

829
00:54:54,985 --> 00:54:56,905
You shouldn't say something so crazy.

830
00:54:56,990 --> 00:55:00,230
Jaechan. You're totally crazy right now.
Do you know that?

831
00:55:01,481 --> 00:55:02,153
No.

832
00:55:02,643 --> 00:55:03,650
I'm totally fine.

833
00:55:04,518 --> 00:55:07,537
If I didn't stop you,
you would've killed that guy.

834
00:55:07,771 --> 00:55:11,795
Since it's you, you would've fabricated
things and framed her for the accident.

835
00:55:11,880 --> 00:55:13,741
Hey. You crazy jerk. That's enough.

836
00:55:13,826 --> 00:55:16,613
That woman would've become a criminal...

837
00:55:17,335 --> 00:55:19,529
...and her mom would've died due to shock.

838
00:55:20,485 --> 00:55:24,821
And that woman would've taken her
life foolishly because of the injustice.

839
00:55:24,926 --> 00:55:25,989
You...

840
00:55:28,150 --> 00:55:30,214
...are totally capable of doing that.

841
00:55:33,964 --> 00:55:35,372
You're still the same.

842
00:55:35,871 --> 00:55:38,502
You still blame other
people and make excuses.

843
00:55:40,187 --> 00:55:42,081
You almost killed us.

844
00:55:44,584 --> 00:55:45,321
No...

845
00:55:46,885 --> 00:55:48,266
I did it to save you.

846
00:56:02,417 --> 00:56:04,016
Who would believe that?

847
00:56:06,831 --> 00:56:07,814
Hongjoo.

848
00:56:09,251 --> 00:56:11,001
Do you believe this crazy jerk's words?

849
00:56:26,317 --> 00:56:27,050
Well.

850
00:56:28,051 --> 00:56:29,486
Who would believe me...

851
00:56:30,731 --> 00:56:32,689
...if I said that
I saw you in my dreams.

852
00:56:35,923 --> 00:56:38,131
You were so sad in my dream...

853
00:56:40,703 --> 00:56:42,730
...so, I came here to change that dream.

854
00:56:45,063 --> 00:56:46,566
No one would believe...

855
00:56:47,579 --> 00:56:48,926
...that I changed the future.

856
00:58:02,197 --> 00:58:03,046
I...

857
00:58:03,882 --> 00:58:05,148
...believe in you.

858
00:58:07,978 --> 00:58:08,948
Because it's me...

859
00:58:10,773 --> 00:58:12,322
...I can believe in you.

860
00:58:21,093 --> 00:58:22,372
Thank you.

861
00:59:34,104 --> 00:59:42,385
"While You Were Sleeping"
